{"tid":1008590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶推「1 分鐘花光百萬」挑戰活動　得獎者以為是詐騙沒接電話","createTime":"2019-02-04T15:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T04:36:04.000Z","uid":51464,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6d5fe297ea925440e24d2a611a76598e33ef97","tid":1008590,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"淘寶之前在大陸推出了 1 分鐘花光 100 萬人民幣（折合約 116.3 萬港元）的「手淘挑戰 1 分鐘花光 100 萬」推廣活動。活動有如超市常見的免費購物活動一樣，幸運兒只要在限定時間內完成網購，即可免「找數」購物。不過，是次推廣活動的第 2 位被抽中的幸運兒，卻誤以為推廣活動是詐騙，放棄了這次免費網購百萬貨品的機會。<br />\n====================<br />\n竟然唔係詐騙！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667601e0c2f8ef4c4e0b75f5d2bd0cd0f21b5575","tid":1008590,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5c9828b2a2fde72e7ad60dec2f9b82d30398c5","tid":1008590,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2266778/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2266778%2F&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=e2dc4d82\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2266778/</a><br />\n補LINK"},{"pid":"379a26dfa4a8ffcfe1ef221d1aa75a69d9ee4830","tid":1008590,"uid":104658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"諗起安德尊"},{"pid":"f9510a86e86d6d27cdaf92152786bdd2369c30ad","tid":1008590,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:21:30